## 🧠 Critical Config Rules

- Never nest `session` under `agents.defaults` — top-level only
- Never remove `commands.useAccessGroups: false` — breaks slash commands
- Never remove `channels.slack.commands.native: true` — breaks slash commands
- `openclaw doctor --fix` — use with caution, always backup `openclaw.json` first
- Config restarts: use SIGUSR1 for parameter changes only
- New model registration: always requires full `docker-compose down && up`
- `.env` changes: require full `down` + `up` to take effect
- `wakeMode: "now"` is mandatory for all cron jobs when heartbeat is disabled

---

## 🗝️ Key Reminders

- `openclaw.json` backup before every change: `cp openclaw.json openclaw.json.backup-$(date +%Y%m%d)`
- Workspace files backed up nightly via git to your private workspace repo
- GitHub PAT expiry: check your token expiry date and renew before it lapses

